text: Karine Boucher (born 28 July 1972) is a French artistic gymnast, born in Orléans. She competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics, and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:People from Orléans Category:French female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1992 Summer Olympics
